---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Breadcrumb from "../components/Breadcrumb.astro";
import CTAStrip from "../components/CTAStrip.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us | Web Design & SEO Agency | doticrosst"
  description="We're a small web design and SEO agency that builds fast, honest websites for small businesses. Specialist division for hairdressers and barbers."
>
  <section class="bg-charcoal py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <Breadcrumb
        items={[
          { label: "Home", href: "/" },
          { label: "About" },
        ]}
      />
      <div class="mt-4 max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent-light">About Us</p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-black text-white sm:text-5xl">Web design agency where detail matters</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
          The name is a play on "dot the i's and cross the t's". Attention to
          detail is what separates a website that works from one that just exists.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-charcoal">Who we are</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          doticrosst is a small web design and SEO agency based in the UK. We build fast,
          clean websites for small businesses, the kind that load in under a
          second, rank locally, and actually bring in enquiries. Every detail matters to us,
          from the code that powers your site to the words that convince your visitors to pick
          up the phone.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          We started with a specialist focus on hairdressers and barbers, an
          industry full of creative people being overcharged for clunky software
          and template websites. That specialist web design agency division is still going
          strong, but we now work with small businesses across the board: tradespeople,
          professional services, retail, health and wellness, and more.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          We don't use page builders. We don't charge for hosting. We don't
          lock you into platforms you can't leave. We hand-code every site,
          build on open tools, and give you something you actually own. That attention
          to detail is what separates a website that works from one that just sits there
          doing nothing.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-black text-charcoal">Why detail matters in web design</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          Most web agencies build with templates and page builders. The result is a website
          that looks like everyone else's, loads slowly, and gets buried in search results.
          We take a different approach because every detail matters, from how quickly your
          images load on a phone over 4G, to whether your heading tags are structured
          correctly for Google, to the exact words on your call-to-action buttons.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          This is a web design agency that sweats the small stuff because that is where
          results live. A one-second improvement in page speed can increase conversions by
          up to 27%. Properly structured local SEO markup can be the difference between
          appearing in the map pack or not. These details compound over time, turning your
          website into your most reliable source of new business.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-black text-charcoal">How we work with clients</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          We keep things simple. You fill in our scoping form, we come back with a clear
          quote within one working day. No lengthy discovery phases, no bloated proposals
          full of jargon. Once we agree on scope, your website is typically live within
          two to three weeks. You review everything before launch and we do not stop until
          you are happy with the result.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          After launch, we offer optional monthly support for content updates, performance
          monitoring, and technical maintenance. There is no lock-in. You can cancel any
          time. Many of our clients stay with us because the support is genuinely useful,
          not because they are trapped by a contract.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          We explain everything in plain English. You will always know what we are building,
          why we are building it, and what it costs. If we think something is not worth your
          money, we will tell you. That level of honesty is rare in this industry, but it is
          how we believe a web design agency should operate.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">Our Values</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-black text-charcoal sm:text-4xl">How we work</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="mb-5 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/10 text-accent transition-all duration-300 group-hover:bg-accent group-hover:text-white">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal">No bloat</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            We don't build things you don't need. Every page, every feature
            earns its place by making you money or saving you time.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="mb-5 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/10 text-accent transition-all duration-300 group-hover:bg-accent group-hover:text-white">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" /><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal">No lock-in</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            You own your website, your code, your content. We build on open
            tools so you're never trapped by a vendor or tied to us.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="mb-5 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/10 text-accent transition-all duration-300 group-hover:bg-accent group-hover:text-white">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal">No jargon</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            We explain things in plain English. You'll always know what we're
            building, why, and what it costs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTAStrip
    heading="Let's have a chat"
    text="No pitch, no pressure. Just a conversation about where your business is and where you want it to go."
    buttonText="Request a Free Quote"
    buttonHref="/get-started/"
  />
</BaseLayout>
